about.summary: A least recently used (LRU) cache implementation

name: pylru
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "pylru" %}
{% set version = "1.2.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 492f934bb98dc6c8b2370c02c95c65516ddc08c8f64d27f70087eb038621d297

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed -vvv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - pylru

about:
  home: https://github.com/jlhutch/pylru
  license: LGPL
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: A least recently used (LRU) cache implementation

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - nehaljwani
